<p>Verified footage and a video released on Hamas’s official channel show masked gunmen publicly executing eight blindfolded, kneeling suspects in Gaza City, with Hamas labeling them “collaborators and outlaws” [abc.net.au#1][lemonde.fr#1][ndtv.com#1]. The killings come as Hamas launches a crackdown to reassert control in parts of the enclave, where its security units have clashed with armed Palestinian clans, according to multiple reports and analysts [lemonde.fr#1][abc.net.au#1][ndtv.com#2]. President Trump has vowed to disarm Hamas and commented on the crackdown, while the Palestinian Authority condemned the executions as “heinous crimes,” and a rights group demanded an end to “extrajudicial and arbitrary executions” [lemonde.fr#1][ndtv.com#2][timesofisrael.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/lsAY0RiWpqpp2MbSejOd2TM8X247wGPbh5OnI86euYO_B46hzo9Z8MqJeNGNQhCiVkdtgHKJtX-r2j9661mWksQm8DFhWtyiUiJy2sc5wmy4UMcbx1vPrNLncZhuJ39PTV-AwutMJ2R3FOBGC8YJrfHhXDXyzZkEMhyFlr77dcY9mMfca05jNolXi5Te8C83zTs4nOGf4CqAeo2VL_GDF8nQMgWevvjGqPX3CG6ALXy25tM-xPAGQqI' alt='Footage circulated online purports to show public executions in Gaza City.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Public executions: Hamas-published footage shows eight blindfolded suspects shot in the street, described by Hamas as “collaborators and outlaws” [lemonde.fr#1][ndtv.com#1].</li><li>Crackdown context: The executions occurred amid a Hamas security crackdown and armed clashes with Palestinian clans in parts of Gaza [lemonde.fr#1][ndtv.com#2].</li><li>Verification notes: Open-source analysis and reporting indicate the scenes were filmed in Gaza City and align with claims of extrajudicial executions [abc.net.au#1].</li><li>US position: President Trump vowed to disarm Hamas, and also downplayed the crackdown in remarks reported by regional media [lemonde.fr#1][timesofisrael.com#1][ndtv.com#2].</li><li>Palestinian response: The Palestinian Authority labeled the executions “heinous crimes,” and a PA rights group called for an immediate halt to extrajudicial killings [timesofisrael.com#1].</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Hamas: In its published video, Hamas labeled those executed as “collaborators and outlaws.”. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2025/10/15/hamas-launches-gaza-crackdown-as-trump-vows-to-disarm-group_6746445_4.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li><li>Palestinian Authority: Abbas’s office condemned the executions as “heinous crimes” and called for the restoration of law. (<a href='https://www.timesofisrael.com/pa-condemns-hamas-executions-as-heinous-crimes-trump-shrugs-off-crackdown/'>The Times of Israel</a>)</li><li>President Trump: The US president vowed to disarm Hamas and, in remarks reported regionally, downplayed the crackdown. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2025/10/15/hamas-launches-gaza-crackdown-as-trump-vows-to-disarm-group_6746445_4.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li><li>PA rights group: The group demanded an end to “extrajudicial and arbitrary executions” in Gaza. (<a href='https://www.timesofisrael.com/pa-condemns-hamas-executions-as-heinous-crimes-trump-shrugs-off-crackdown/'>The Times of Israel</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-10-15/abc-news-verify-hamas-executions-gaza-city/105893350'>Graphic footage shows Hamas executing people in the streets of Gaza</a> - abc.net.au</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/hamas-brutally-executes-8-gazans-on-camera-amid-donald-trumps-disarm-warning-9458416#publisher=newsstand'>Hamas Brutally Executes 8 Gazans In Public Amid Trump&#x27;s &#x27;Disarm&#x27; Warning</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2025/10/15/hamas-launches-gaza-crackdown-as-trump-vows-to-disarm-group_6746445_4.html'>Hamas launches Gaza crackdown as Trump vows to disarm group</a> - lemonde.fr</li><li><a href='https://www.rt.com/news/626437-hamas-execution-gaza-videos/'>Hamas executes seven men in Gaza (GRAPHIC 